;26 inchat
 mysc GLOBAL ckbxs GLOBAL ut GLOBAL yhtz GLOBAL
rollt GLOBAL myturn GLOBAL co GLOBAL dd GLOBAL dt GLOBAL
{ { 0 SWAP SETSPOTSTATE } [ 7 8 9 10 11 12] FOREACH
 1 myturn = 13 sp = ckbxs tckbxs =
